===========================
bc_l - a simple twitter bot
===========================

bc_l is a quick python interface to the 'bc -l' command.

It accepts input via twitter direct message (dm) and returns output via a mention (@) the requesting user.

Created by Hilary Mason (@hmason) and inspired by Chris Wiggins (@chrishwiggins).


